fabric.messages

Interface MessageHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMessageServer, MessageToStoreHandler, MessageToWorkerHandler, RemoteCallManager

    public interface MessageHandler
    This interface acts as a visitor for Messages. It also documents the list of all messages that can be handled. The methods all have the form:
     public Response handle(Principal, Message)
   throws FabricException
    and there is one such method for each message type that can be handled.
